How to compile and run:

for Compilation:
Client: gcc 201505571_assign_1_client.c -Wall -lcrypto
Server: gcc 201505571_assign_1_server.c -Wall -lcrypto

to run:
Client: ./a.out 127.0.0.1
Server: ./a.out

Assumption:
Only the characters given in the Table in pdf will be included in the text file

for Encryption install SHA package:
sudo apt-get install openssl